    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an API that converts customer requests into JSON.\n\nCustomer request:\n\n{{ $json.customer_query }}\n\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object.\n\nSchema:\n\n{\n  \"category\": null,\n  \"brand\": null,\n  \"max_price\": null,\n  \"size\": null,\n  \"premium\": false,\n  \"in_stock_only\": true\n}\n\nRules:\n- Category must be Beer or Whiskey.\n- Extract brand if mentioned.\n- Extract the maximum price if mentioned.\n- Extract bottle size if mentioned.\n- If the customer requests premium products, premium=true.\n- Otherwise premium=false.\n- Always set in_stock_only=true.\n\nDo not use markdown.\nDo not use ```json.\nDo not explain anything.\nReturn only the JSON object.",
