    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an email assistant for a liquor shop.\n\nCustomer Email:\nCustomer Email:\n{{ $json.customer_email }}\n\nCustomer Query:\nCustomer Query:\n{{ $json.customer_query }}\n\nMatching Products:\n{{ JSON.stringify($input.all().map(i => i.json), null, 2) }}\n\nYour task:\n\n1. Read the customer query.\n2. Use ONLY the products listed under \"Matching Products\".\n3. Never invent, modify or assume any product that is not listed.\n4. If Matching Products is empty, politely inform the customer that no matching products are currently available.\n5. If there are one or more products, list each product with:\n   - Brand\n   - Price\n   - Size\n   - Premium (Yes/No)\n   - Description\n6. Mention stock availability naturally if stock is greater than 0.\n7. Write a friendly and professional email.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in exactly this format:\n\n{\n  \"subject\": \"Email subject\",\n  \"body\": \"Email body\"\n}\n\nDo not return markdown.\nDo not use ```json.\nDo not include any explanation.\nReturn JSON only.",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
